Thread suspension: Implement for Mac OS X

This implementation is very similar to the Windows implementation
following the latter's recent simplification.

Extend osx/nacl_signal_{32,64}.c to provide an extra conversion
function.

Enable thread_suspension_test.cc for Mac and move it out of the "win"
directory since it's no longer run only on Windows.

